## âš¡ Quick Start

### **1. Start Services**

```bash
# Backend (Docker)
docker-compose up -d

# Frontend (Dashboard)
cd dashboard-ui && npm run dev
```

### **2. Open Dashboard**

```
http://localhost:3000
```

### **3. Run Demo**

```bash
python3 sdk-python/examples/realtime_streaming_demo.py
```

**Watch decisions appear in real-time!** âœ¨

